:"我以前都係<br />\n<br />\n但得35k<br />\n<br />\n跟住學人玩成家立室<br />\n<br />\n然後...就沒有然後了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ab61c2005e9960903f453da7b810f0cb9057927","tid":39803,"uid":6193,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T02:55:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>嘗試笑到四萬咁口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有創意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28a7cb23b05d3c37e05476e9c1f8160086c6e647","tid":39803,"uid":33508,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T02:56:11.000Z","msg":"讀Master<br />\n助養<br />\n做長線投資"},{"pid":"4223b9bb17af88ae1cce9082e1b93b6d2250c6a7","tid":39803,"uid":50856,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T02:57:52.000Z","msg":"學資產管理，諗辦法財務自由"},{"pid":"a9a3f032fb3215b42af9d2c9e210077d6a76d6af","tid":39803,"uid":12827,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T02:57:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我以前都係<br />\n<br />\n但得35k<br />\n<br />\n跟住學人玩成家立室<br />\n<br />\n然後...就沒有然後了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n+1<br />\n45k<br />\n沒然後了"},{"pid":"d6dac65538c9f7c7a83ccec637c0e5f02369f1b6","tid":39803,"uid":15859,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T02:58:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我已經放咗係學術台...<br />\n畀吓面認真答丫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n動機係希望脫離月入四五萬呢個層次<br />\n或者進入另一種生活模式<br />\n總之要走出框框<br />\n<br />\n再讀degree<br />\n讀Master<br />\n養車<br />\n培養燒錢興趣？<br />\n信耶穌？<br />\n信佛？<br />\n創業？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實四 五萬再加你無家庭負擔<br />\n個生活層次做唔做到<br />\n有車 有樓<br />\n想飛就飛去旅行<br />\n去酒吧飲野諗到就叫<br />\n<br />\n除左唔可以好土豪咁<br />\n話買名牌比女就買<br />\n買馬 買遊艇 買飛機 之外<br />\n同派錢買game比身邊朋友同你玩之外<br />\n（其實派game都唔叫貴）<br />\n<br />\n下一個生活層次如果係做馬會會員的話<br />\n都真係幾遠<br />\n<br />\n或者話，打工係去唔到/ 你要做你行業既一哥<br />\n<br />\n四 五皮應該叫專業人士入面既中流<br />\n睇你咩行業要再上要咩資格<br />\n醫生 律師的話就做個專科再打靚自己個名<br />\n<br />\n你不如透露下你做邊行再分析下<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但呢個gap係好大我認為<br />\n賺五萬同十萬好似差一倍<br />\n而呢個差距係打工階級上流到<br />\n但如果講生活，無家庭負擔下應該無咩大分別🤔<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申 窮撚"},{"pid":"0a675a8b8106f536ed732284facf77157a74035d","tid":39803,"uid":1037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T02:59:23.000Z","msg":"做我男朋友<br />\n養我一世<br />\n有家庭有小朋友就真係成功喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ccc5918eac955b78798cf453342aa3db899395df","tid":39803,"uid":52949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T02:59:52.000Z","msg":"每月拎三萬助養我<br />\n<br />\n咁你就跳出到個框框"},{"pid":"768e031f4305bd74556be9d86753e91f6e0baafd","tid":39803,"uid":1227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T03:04:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>做我男朋友<br />\n養我一世<br />\n有家庭有小朋友就真係成功喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n笑大人個口"},{"pid":"4b21408425b017fef3b2dde4cacb461acbca92bd","tid":39803,"uid":5148,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T03:16:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>儲起佢，買基金<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 以備不時之需<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n基金</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n買基金有咩問題？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n買開果隻每月有派息，一年有5里<br />\n隻基金本身仲升緊"},{"pid":"042d7ea07b17a1f52b7e03e5b1dd50dfc9eaf0ef","tid":39803,"uid":28068,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T03:38:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>每月拎三萬助養我<br />\n<br />\n咁你就跳出到個框框</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實樓主都可能係俾人助養"},{"pid":"e0bb4c28bf0d61b29470bd3c2de2c27681c3ec74","tid":39803,"uid":50856,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T04:15:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>儲起佢，買基金<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 以備不時之需<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n基金</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n買基金有咩問題？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n買開果隻每月有派息，一年有5里<br />\n隻基金本身仲升緊</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢響個本度拎返比你洗咋....條款係咁寫"}]}